me.leoko.advancedgui.utils

Class GuiInstance

  • java.lang.Object
    • me.leoko.advancedgui.utils.GuiInstance
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    GuiItemInstance, GuiWallInstance

    public abstract class GuiInstance
extends Object
    A GuiInstance manages Interactions of Players with a Layout and renders and sends the corresponding frames.
